verbose_text: Herein, we demonstrated that miR-433 over-expression enhanced both cardiac fibroblast proliferation and their differentiation into myofibroblasts, whereas inhibition of miR-433 attenuated these processes, indicating the critical stimulatory effect of miR-433 on cardiac fibroblast activation.
evidence: miR-433 over-expression enhanced both cardiac fibroblast proliferation and their differentiation
